OL,3,CNew rules announced to protect public
OL,4,Cas fire and rescue workers strike
OL,6,FNew rules have been announced aimed at
OL,7,Fensuring fire and rescue services are
OL,8,Fable to use 73% of their fire engines
OL,9,Fduring strikes.
OL,11,FThe government said the move will
OL,12,Fensure the public are protected from
OL,13,Fthe "dangerous impact" of striking
OL,14,Ffire and rescue service staff.
OL,16,FThe Fire Brigades Union (FBU) said it
OL,17,Fwill resist the "outrageous"
OL,18,Fregulation.
