OL,3,CNew rules announced to protect public
OL,4,Cas fire and rescue workers strike
OL,6,FThe government said that during any
OL,7,Fstrike, fire and rescue services (FRS)
OL,8,Fwill be expected to crew 73% of fire
OL,9,Fengines and other vehicles that they
OL,10,Fwould normally have available.
OL,12,FThe fire brigade will also be expected
OL,13,Fto attend all emergencies as usual,
OL,14,Feven during a strike period.
OL,16,FThe regulation will be enforced once a
OL,17,Funion has informed a FRS that it
OL,18,Fintends to strike and the employer
OL,19,Ftakes action.
