OL,6,FThe employer can issue a work notice
OL,7,Fthat tells the union which members of
OL,8,Fthe FRS will be required to work to
OL,9,Fmeet the minimum service level, and
OL,10,Fthe work they will be required to do.
OL,12,FFire control rooms will also be
OL,13,Fexpected to have enough staff to
OL,14,Fmaintain their important functions and
OL,15,Frespond to 999 calls and major
OL,16,Fincidents.
