OL,6,F"While it is right that workers have
OL,7,Fthe ability to strike, this must not
OL,8,Fcome at the cost of public safety. The
OL,9,Fnew minimum service level for fire and
OL,10,Frescue will help save lives."
OL,12,FMatt Wrack, general secretary of the
OL,13,FFBU, said: "This is an outrageous and
OL,14,Fauthoritarian plan to seek to ban
OL,15,Fstrikes in the fire and rescue
OL,16,Fservice. The government wants this in
OL,17,Fplace so that it can attack the pay
OL,18,Fand conditions of firefighters and
OL,19,Fother workers.
