OL,4,Cas fire and rescue workers strike
OL,6,F"It's one of the worst assaults in the
OL,7,Flast century on the rights of working
OL,8,Fpeople to defend themselves.
OL,10,F"The Fire Brigades Union will resist
OL,11,Fthis dictatorial legislation in every
OL,12,Fway possible."
OL,14,FSo-called minimum service levels have
OL,15,Falready been introduced in the rail
OL,16,Findustry but were not used by any
OL,17,Fcompanies hit by a recent train
OL,18,Fdrivers' strike.
