OL,6,FTUC General Secretary Paul Nowak said:
OL,7,F"This is a flagrant attack on the
OL,8,Fright to strike of firefighters.
OL,10,F"No one should be sacked for
OL,11,Fexercising their right to strike, but
OL,12,Fthat is exactly what the government is
OL,13,Fthreatening.
OL,15,F"These new laws are undemocratic,
OL,16,Funworkable and are likely illegal and
OL,17,Fthey will do nothing to resolve
OL,18,Findustrial disputes.
